{"tid":2158390,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"純粹呻下","createTime":"2020-08-15T16:35:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-16T03:58:54.000Z","uid":54018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"11c9fa8d83b6f7fc9f2195f1aeb490d81f817112","tid":2158390,"uid":54018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T16:35:41.000Z","msg":"有時拍拖，拍到覺得自己一個人都搞得掂所有野<br />\n唔主動出去搵對方、對方就唔會主動出去搵自己<br />\n同過佢講  有時可唔可以主動黎搵下我<br />\n可能當下話可以，到最後放假都係自己一個人<br />\n佢就話出街都唔知做咩好，外面又多肺炎<br />\n久而久之，已經無左搵佢既動力同期待。明知對方都唔會做到，又何必一而再再而三講，令到大家唔開心。<br />\n每日都係例行公事報早午晚三餐，早抖晚安。<br />\n以家唯有發展下其他方面，諗下點搵錢，時間可能會好過少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申男，唔會分手"},{"pid":"8097e44b1df98677766c4c152edf3078cbaf90f1","tid":2158390,"uid":37397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T16:43:21.000Z","msg":"對方做唔到嘅話，可以考慮自己主動做，唔需要擔心對方反應唔熱切而卻步。熱情感染熱情。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce8bc25d707c9cbb0b7948124fd4dfb52f79ba98","tid":2158390,"uid":218575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T17:26:45.000Z","msg":"唔要嘅俾我"},{"pid":"97305f215b14b62443ee1eaaf46322c9ea637da4","tid":2158390,"uid":343239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T17:45:54.000Z","msg":"屌下佢就醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bffab7ebb83c388214a6f97ab6a3684b8b5680f5","tid":2158390,"uid":54018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8097e44b1df98677766c4c152edf3078cbaf90f1","tid":2158390,"uid":37397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T16:43:21.000Z","msg":"對方做唔到嘅話，可以考慮自己主動做，唔需要擔心對方反應唔熱切而卻步。熱情感染熱情。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T02:50:52.000Z","msg":"主動左兩年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f92fd7e74d0c7c6c04d3e60f1c2f28ff0ce5849a","tid":215